Localization.Name: R6 Pro
Localization.Description: R6 Pro's rugged footwear is made to withstand wear and tear in even the most extreme environments, so even if you get knocked down, we're there to help you get back up again.

Localization.Name: Tona Shoes Dark Red
Localization.Description: Perfect for hiking or fieldwork, the Tona from R6 Pro is a low-top sneaker built out of breathable Cheofreme materials which not only provide extra protection against impacts, but keep your feet dry.
